<i>Gonna live forever.</i>

20:01.199 --> 20:02.117
<i>Bon appétit.</i>

20:12.461 --> 20:13.754
Well, fuck.

20:15.923 --> 20:18.008
I think I can speak
on behalf of my people.

20:18.759 --> 20:19.968
We’ve had enough spaghetti.

20:20.928 --> 20:22.387
You did it, didn’t you.

20:22.387 --> 20:25.140
You couldn’t change everyone’s taste,
but you could make it...

20:26.058 --> 20:26.975
distasteful.

20:27.559 --> 20:30.187
- It wasn’t the death, was it?
- It was the complexity of life.

20:30.520 --> 20:31.730
God, what was the point?

20:31.730 --> 20:34.399
If you’re asking whether this was
a story about right and wrong,

20:34.399 --> 20:36.652
the answer is, I don’t care.

20:37.194 --> 20:39.154
- So what do we do?
- Cells consume, Morty.

20:39.154 --> 20:41.657
Life itself is wrong,
and that means death is right.

20:42.074 --> 20:43.241
But you can’t side with that.

20:43.575 --> 20:45.869
So you live, even when it means eating.

20:46.578 --> 20:48.413
And Fred here really did it well.

20:55.045 --> 20:57.339
The hell is this?
Where is the spaghetti?

20:57.339 --> 20:58.882
Why don’t you go fuck yourself, Summer?

20:58.882 --> 21:00.467
- What?
- What’s wrong with Salisbury Steaks?

21:00.467 --> 21:01.468
At least try them.

21:01.843 --> 21:03.261
Holy shit, this is...

21:03.720 --> 21:06.473
the best Salisbury steak I’ve ever had.

21:07.057 --> 21:08.684
Is it actually Salisbury steak?

21:09.434 --> 21:10.894
Do you want to know or not?

21:10.894 --> 21:12.354
No thanks!

21:12.354 --> 21:14.773
Just so you know, it’s really bad.

21:14.773 --> 21:17.776
- Whatever you say.
- Seriously, I’m not kidding.

21:17.776 --> 21:20.487
I won’t tell you but I need you
to know the truth is horrible

21:20.487 --> 21:23.240
so that if you ever find out on accident
you can’t blame me.

21:23.240 --> 21:24.324
Now that’s a deal.

21:25.200 --> 21:26.868
Honestly if you knew
you might kill yourselves,

21:26.868 --> 21:28.870
- that’s the last thing I’ll say forever.
- Good!

22:08.660 --> 22:11.371
